WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.270
Amen. He said there's going to be a new

00:00:02.280 --> 00:00:04.710
wave of patriotism coming out, and that's

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:07.349
whenever I saw Trump and I saw

00:00:07.359 --> 00:00:11.150
a red wave coming out of Michigan.

00:00:11.160 --> 00:00:12.950
Then I saw Oklahoma, and there

00:00:12.950 --> 00:00:12.960
were

00:00:12.960 --> 00:00:15.709
embers of people;

00:00:15.719 --> 00:00:17.670
they had torches all

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:18.870
throughout Oklahoma and they were

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.550
raising up these torches that looked

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.870
like fire. They were bringing forth a

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:25.790
new patriotism upon the nation, and it

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:27.429
was being birthed and

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:29.550
just kept spreading like fire all

00:00:29.560 --> 00:00:31.109
throughout America. I

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:33.869
saw Trump rising up, and then I saw an

00:00:33.879 --> 00:00:37.150
attempt on his life. This bullet

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:40.590
flew by his ear, and it came so close to

00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:43.549
his head that it busted his eardrum.

00:00:43.559 --> 00:00:46.630
He fell to his knees

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:48.910
during this timeframe and he started

00:00:48.910 --> 00:00:48.920
worshipping

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:51.029
the Lord. He got radically

00:00:51.039 --> 00:00:53.590
born again during this timeframe. I'm

00:00:53.590 --> 00:00:53.600
talking—people

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:56.229
say he's saved now, but he

00:00:56.239 --> 00:00:59.509
becomes really on fire for Jesus

00:00:59.509 --> 00:00:59.519
from

00:00:59.519 --> 00:01:02.189
what I saw coming. Then I saw

00:01:02.199 --> 00:01:05.030
people interceding.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:08.030
I saw him winning the presidency. The

00:01:08.030 --> 00:01:08.040
Lord showed

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.190
me it

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:12.149
would go clear into the summer; great

00:01:12.159 --> 00:01:14.149
persecution would come on him through

00:01:14.159 --> 00:01:16.630
the judges,

00:01:16.640 --> 00:01:18.310
the law, and all these people trying to

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:19.870
sue him, but there

00:01:19.880 --> 00:01:21.749
would be a stop to it. Things

00:01:21.759 --> 00:01:23.990
would start to break free

00:01:23.990 --> 00:01:24.000
coming

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.870
toward the fall, and then I saw him

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:28.789
winning the election through

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:30.670
the patriots coming out and voting.

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:32.270
Then there will be a

00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:35.030
great economic crash. I saw they had a

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:38.590
great economic plan, a crash worse than

00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:40.990
the Great Depression. The Lord

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.190
warned me about this; it would be a great

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:46.469
dark time. But I saw paddles coming upon

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:48.990
America's soil like a shocking of the

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:52.030
soil. I saw Donald Trump praying in

00:01:52.040 --> 00:01:54.630
the Oval Office, and

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.950
he was weeping before the Lord with his

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:58.469
hands on his head. He was

00:01:58.479 --> 00:02:00.950
weeping, and there were ministers and

00:02:00.950 --> 00:02:00.960
people—I

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:02.029
don't know if they were

00:02:02.039 --> 00:02:04.230
senators or

00:02:04.230 --> 00:02:04.240
congresspeople—I

00:02:04.240 --> 00:02:06.990
just saw them pacing

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:10.029
back and forth inside

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:14.309
the Oval

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:16.350
Office, and they were interceding all

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.830
inside there. I could feel the

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.550
presence of the Lord so strong on this.

00:02:19.560 --> 00:02:21.430
Then I could see that darkness that

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:24.150
was the heaviness upon America with the

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:28.309
financial crisis

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:30.470
of what I saw coming; it started to

00:02:30.480 --> 00:02:33.070
lift above the trees. I saw the blue

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:34.750
and the things coming back out,

00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:36.910
and the green times and good times

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:38.670
coming back again. But the Lord said it

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:42.149
would be a season of

00:02:42.159 --> 00:02:44.509
a shaking, and it would be a shaking to

00:02:44.519 --> 00:02:47.670
awaken.

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:50.750
Basically, He was not done

00:02:50.760 --> 00:02:52.229
with America; there would be a great

00:02:52.239 --> 00:02:54.309
revival. It's not

00:02:54.319 --> 00:02:55.630
all doom and gloom—that's what He said.

00:02:55.640 --> 00:02:57.830
The sky is not falling. It's just a

00:02:57.830 --> 00:02:57.840
time—it's

00:02:57.840 --> 00:03:00.070
like people would say this is

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:01.910
judgment, and the Lord said, "Do not call

00:03:01.920 --> 00:03:03.830
this judgment. It's not my judgment; it's

00:03:03.840 --> 00:03:08.360
a correction."There's a correction coming.

